g.com/thread/1490363\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1490363</a><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n10月1日全球港人大遊行<br />\nWe should book the Victoria Park now<br />\nSo that the pro-china groups cannot use the Victoria Park to celebrate<br />\n</span></span></strong></div><br />\nThe Chinese government does not want us to march on 1 Oct., so we must have  10月1日全球港人大遊行."}]}